I"2<ol>
  <li>Install <a href="https://www.raspberrypi.org/downloads/raspbian/"><em>Raspbian</em></a> to SD
card.</li>
  <li>Create file <code class="highlighter-rouge">ssh</code> on <em>boot</em> partition:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">touch</span> /Volumes/boot/ssh
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Power-on Raspberry.</li>
  <li>Connect Raspberry to Ethernet cable on DHCP enabled network.</li>
  <li>Scan Network with <code class="highlighter-rouge">nmap</code> for Raspberry:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">sudo </span>nmap <span class="nt">-sP</span> 192.168.1.0/24 | <span class="nb">awk</span> <span class="s1">'/^Nmap/{ip=$NF}/B8:27:EB/{print ip}'</span>
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Connect to Raspberry via SSH (username: <code class="highlighter-rouge">pi</code>, password: <code class="highlighter-rouge">raspberry</code>).</li>
</ol>

